Package ohos.ai.cv.common

Class CvPoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.ai.cv.common.CvPoint
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Sequenceable

    public class CvPoint
extends Object
implements Sequenceable
    Describes location information of an image in a two-dimensional coordinate system.

    The location information includes the horizontal and vertical coordinates.
